  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q001059.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) E-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , who makes the foreign lands submit to Ninĝirsu , subjugated Elam and Subartu to Ninĝirsu ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001059.9",
      "line_range": "9",
      "translation": "(ii 4) He built the temple of Tiraš and made it resplendent for him ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001059.12",
      "line_range": "12",
      "translation": "(ii 7) E-ana-tum , who submits to the orders of Ninĝirsu , is someone , who has no opponent throughout all lands by the might of Ninĝirsu ."
    }
  ],
